title: Tailor Swif

description.plain:
The song “Tailor Swif” was first performed at Rolling Loud Portugal on July 7th, 2022. The song leaked in full alongside the music video on July 9th, 2022. Then performed again at the Positivus Festival on July 16th, 2022.

Rocky confirmed in 2023 that the song won’t appear on the album due to it leaking but played it at Rolling Loud Miami 2023 not long after. The song’s cover art appeared on merch and Rocky’s Instagram in early 2023, but nothing ever came from this until the reworked song and cover were leaked in September of 2023. Revealed by Mod to have always been titled “Tailor Swif”.

On August 30th, 2024, the song saw an official release on streaming platforms.

On November 8th, 2024, the song’s music video received a Grammy nomination in the Best Music Video category, which is A$AP Rocky’s first since 2016.
